{
  "i18n": true,
  "type": "tabs",
  "items": {
    "general": {
      "type": "panel",
      "label": {
        "en": "General",
        "de": "Allgemein"
      },
      "items": {
        "intro": {
          "type": "staticText",
          "newLine": true,
          "sm": 12,
          "text": {
            "en": "Outgoing messages are sent via open-wa using sendTo(instance, 'send', {to, text}). Incoming replies can either be delivered through the configured state path or via sendTo('reminder.X', 'incoming', payload). Optional wa.me links can be generated so the child or parent can just tap a link and send the prepared reply.",
            "de": "Ausgehende Nachrichten werden über open-wa mit sendTo(instance, 'send', {to, text}) gesendet. Eingehende Antworten können entweder über den konfigurierten State-Pfad oder per sendTo('reminder.X', 'incoming', payload) angeliefert werden. Optional können wa.me-Links erzeugt werden, damit Kind oder Papa nur noch auf einen Link tippen und die vorbereitete Antwort senden müssen."
          }
        },
        "openWaInstance": {
          "type": "instance",
          "adapter": "open-wa",
          "label": {
            "en": "open-wa instance",
            "de": "open-wa Instanz"
          },
          "sm": 4
        },
        "incomingStateId": {
          "type": "text",
          "label": {
            "en": "Incoming message state ID",
            "de": "State-ID für eingehende Nachrichten"
          },
          "sm": 4
        },
        "replyLinkPhone": {
          "type": "text",
          "label": {
            "en": "WhatsApp number for click-to-reply links",
            "de": "WhatsApp-Nummer für Klick-Antworten"
          },
          "help": {
            "en": "Optional. Enter the number of the WhatsApp account behind open-wa in international format without spaces, for example 491791514520. The adapter will build wa.me links that already contain the reply text.",
            "de": "Optional. Trage die Nummer des WhatsApp-Kontos hinter open-wa im internationalen Format ohne Leerzeichen ein, z. B. 491791514520. Der Adapter baut dann wa.me-Links mit bereits vorbereiteter Antwort."
          },
          "sm": 4
        },
        "historyLimit": {
          "type": "number",
          "label": {
            "en": "History entries to keep",
            "de": "Anzahl Historieneinträge"
          },
          "min": 10,
          "max": 1000,
          "sm": 3
        },
        "logIncomingMessages": {
          "type": "checkbox",
          "label": {
            "en": "Store last incoming message in info.lastIncoming",
            "de": "Letzte eingehende Nachricht in info.lastIncoming speichern"
          },
          "sm": 9
        }
      }
    },
    "tasksPanel": {
      "type": "panel",
      "label": {
        "en": "Tasks",
        "de": "Aufgaben"
      },
      "items": {
        "tasksHint": {
          "type": "staticText",
          "newLine": true,
          "sm": 12,
          "text": {
            "en": "Each task now opens as a separate card so the fields are easier to read and edit. For replies use the exact WhatsApp chat ID when needed. If your incoming payload uses values like ...@lid, copy exactly that value from info.lastIncoming instead of only the phone number.",
            "de": "Jede Aufgabe öffnet sich jetzt als eigene Karte, damit die Felder besser lesbar und editierbar sind. Für Antworten verwende bei Bedarf die exakte WhatsApp-Chat-ID. Wenn im eingehenden Payload Werte wie ...@lid auftauchen, kopiere genau diesen Wert aus info.lastIncoming statt nur der Telefonnummer."
          }
        },
        "tasks": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "sm": 12,
          "clone": "id",
          "titleAttr": "title",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "checkbox",
              "attr": "enabled",
              "label": {
                "en": "Task active",
                "de": "Aufgabe aktiv"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 3,
              "default": true,
              "newLine": true
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "id",
              "label": {
                "en": "Internal ID",
                "de": "Interne ID"
              },
              "help": {
                "en": "Use a stable short ID, for example treppe.",
                "de": "Verwende eine stabile kurze ID, z. B. treppe."
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 3,
              "default": "task-1"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "title",
              "label": {
                "en": "Title",
                "de": "Titel"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 6,
              "default": "Treppe absaugen"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "message",
              "label": {
                "en": "Message text",
                "de": "Nachrichtentext"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 12,
              "default": "Bitte die Treppe absaugen.",
              "minRows": 2,
              "maxRows": 4,
              "newLine": true
            },
            {
              "type": "select",
              "attr": "weekday",
              "label": {
                "en": "Weekday",
                "de": "Wochentag"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 6,
              "md": 3,
              "default": 3,
              "options": [
                { "label": { "en": "Sunday", "de": "Sonntag" }, "value": 0 },
                { "label": { "en": "Monday", "de": "Montag" }, "value": 1 },
                { "label": { "en": "Tuesday", "de": "Dienstag" }, "value": 2 },
                { "label": { "en": "Wednesday", "de": "Mittwoch" }, "value": 3 },
                { "label": { "en": "Thursday", "de": "Donnerstag" }, "value": 4 },
                { "label": { "en": "Friday", "de": "Freitag" }, "value": 5 },
                { "label": { "en": "Saturday", "de": "Samstag" }, "value": 6 }
              ],
              "newLine": true
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "time",
              "label": {
                "en": "Time (HH:mm)",
                "de": "Uhrzeit (HH:mm)"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 6,
              "md": 3,
              "default": "17:00"
            },
            {
              "type": "number",
              "attr": "childReminderHours",
              "label": {
                "en": "Reminder interval child (hours)",
                "de": "Erinnerungsintervall Kind (Stunden)"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 6,
              "md": 3,
              "default": 3,
              "min": 1,
              "max": 168
            },
            {
              "type": "number",
              "attr": "parentReminderHours",
              "label": {
                "en": "Reminder interval parent (hours)",
                "de": "Erinnerungsintervall Papa (Stunden)"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 6,
              "md": 3,
              "default": 3,
              "min": 1,
              "max": 168
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "childChatId",
              "label": {
                "en": "Child chat ID",
                "de": "Chat-ID Kind"
              },
              "help": {
                "en": "Use the exact incoming value, for example 165235998597365@lid.",
                "de": "Verwende den exakten eingehenden Wert, z. B. 165235998597365@lid."
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 6,
              "newLine": true,
              "default": "4917012345678@c.us"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "parentChatId",
              "label": {
                "en": "Parent chat ID",
                "de": "Chat-ID Papa"
              },
              "help": {
                "en": "Use the exact incoming value from info.lastIncoming.",
                "de": "Verwende den exakten eingehenden Wert aus info.lastIncoming."
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 6,
              "default": "4917099999999@c.us"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "childKeywords",
              "label": {
                "en": "Child keywords",
                "de": "Schlüsselwörter Kind"
              },
              "help": {
                "en": "Comma separated, for example erledigt,fertig,done",
                "de": "Kommagetrennt, z. B. erledigt,fertig,done"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 6,
              "newLine": true,
              "default": "erledigt,fertig,done"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "parentKeywords",
              "label": {
                "en": "Parent keywords",
                "de": "Schlüsselwörter Papa"
              },
              "help": {
                "en": "Comma separated, for example ja,bestaetigt,bestätigt,ok",
                "de": "Kommagetrennt, z. B. ja,bestaetigt,bestätigt,ok"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 6,
              "default": "ja,bestaetigt,bestätigt,ok"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
